          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "When the action executes, the node’s ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.spritekit/documentation/SpriteKit/SKNode/position",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " and ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.spritekit/documentation/SpriteKit/SKNode/zRotation",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " properties are animated along the provided path.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "This action is reversible; the resulting action creates a reversed path and then follows it, with the same duration.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
